<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Travel Journal - <%= destination %></title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@4.12.24/dist/full.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css"/>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="hero min-h-screen" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506157786151-b8491531f063?q=80&w=2340&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D'); 
  background-size: cover; 
  background-position: center;">
    <div class="hero-overlay bg-opacity-60"></div>
    <div class="hero-content text-neutral-content text-center">
      <div class="max-w-lg">
        <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold"><%= destination %></h1>
        <p class="mb-5">
          St. John's is the perfect combination of big-city luxury and traditional small-town charm. It is
          one of the oldest and most easterly cities in North America, and has become a rare destination
          full of character and charisma, with a contemporary, sophisticated edge.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto my-6 gap-x-8">
    <div class="flex justify-end mb-4">
      <a href="/memories/add" class="btn btn-active btn-primary">Add Location</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <table class="table">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-neutral-content">
            <th></th>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Address</th>
            <th>Comments</th>
            <th></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% locations.forEach(location => { %>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <img src="<%= location.image || 'https://via.placeholder.com/150' %>" class="w-96">
              </td>
              <td>
                <span class="font-bold"><%= location.name %></span>
                <br>
                <span class="badge badge-primary badge-sm badge-outline"><%= location.category %></span>
              </td>
              <td><%= location.address %></td>
              <td><%= location.comments %></td>
              <td>
                <a href="/memories/delete/<%= location.id %>" class="btn btn-default btn-xs">delete</a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% }) %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>